0:02:23.300,0:02:28.100
Your Majesties, Lady Cao is here with Princess Wenyi.

0:02:28.100,0:02:31.200
I hope they didn't feel unwell
walking under the the blazing sun.

0:02:31.200,0:02:32.640
Show her in quickly.

0:02:45.860,0:02:50.100
Grace to Your Majesties.

0:02:50.800,0:02:52.020
It's scorching hot at this time.

0:02:52.500,0:02:56.000
Why did you go out with the princess?

0:02:56.000,0:02:57.860
Can she handle the heat even if you can stand it?

0:02:57.860,0:02:59.520
I do apologize, Your Majesty.

0:02:59.520,0:03:02.800
The princess has been crying for the entire morning.

0:03:02.800,0:03:06.800
I thought she must be missing Her Majesty.
[The empress is the nominal mother of all imperial children.]

0:03:06.800,0:03:10.300
No worries, I miss Wenyi as well.

0:03:10.300,0:03:12.340
Come here, I'll hold her.

0:03:20.960,0:03:24.560
She seems to have lost weight from last time.

0:03:24.560,0:03:27.980
The summer heat spoils her appetite.
She hasn't been eating well lately.

0:03:30.000,0:03:33.000
Wenyi is vulnerable to the heat.

0:03:33.000,0:03:34.840
I'm afraid the concubines are struggling as well.

0:03:34.840,0:03:38.940
How about we move to the
Summer Palace to escape the heat?

0:03:39.000,0:03:42.900
The Summer Palace is well maintained.
Your Majesty can depart at any time.

0:03:42.900,0:03:45.360
I'd like to stay there for some time.

0:03:45.360,0:03:48.780
I haven't been there for 2 years
due to the mourning period for the prior emperor.

0:03:49.000,0:03:51.140
Moving is not going to be too difficult.

0:03:51.140,0:03:53.560
But the Summer Palace cannot accommodate all the concubines?

0:03:53.560,0:03:55.540
Which ones would Your Majesty go with?

0:03:56.780,0:03:59.240
They two are out of question.

0:03:59.240,0:04:04.000
Mothers of the princes and princesses
will follow to take care of the children.

0:04:05.220,0:04:07.540
And Concubine Estime.
That will be all.

0:04:07.540,0:04:13.400
Consort Honnête is in poor health.
She should go with us for her recovery.

0:04:13.500,0:04:15.360
(sigh) Of course.

0:04:15.360,0:04:16.940
As for Consort Fleur ...

0:04:18.260,0:04:21.120
I suggest she stay to take care of the palace.

0:04:23.280,0:04:25.000
This hairpin ...

0:04:25.400,0:04:28.540
I remember this is my gist for Consort Fleur.

0:04:29.000,0:04:30.440
Yes,

0:04:30.440,0:04:33.600
the princess is always happy to see
Her Highness wearing this hairpin.

0:04:33.600,0:04:37.900
So Her Highness gave it to me to play with Wenyi.

0:04:40.620,0:04:42.280
Consort Fleur is going as well.

0:04:42.280,0:04:44.180
Certainly.

0:06:49.000,0:06:52.180
Who was the thoughtful mind
to have arranged all this for me?

0:06:52.180,0:06:57.100
His Majesty wished to have your room scented 
without burning incense on such a hot day.

0:06:57.100,0:07:03.360
At His Majesty's behest, we arranged
flowers and the rotating fan for you, My Lady.

0:07:09.020,0:07:10.880
What a sweet and cooling breeze!

0:07:10.880,0:07:15.040
The rotating fan is exclusive for you
among all the concubines, My Lady.

0:07:16.000,0:07:19.220
What an ingenious design!
His Majesty devoted so much thought to it.

0:07:19.220,0:07:22.300
During the canicular days [hottest period of the year],

0:07:22.340,0:07:24.940
ice will be sent to your chamber from the ice house.

0:07:24.940,0:07:27.680
It will waft coolness to your heart's delight.

0:07:27.900,0:07:33.620
His Majesty ordered us to send you ice
immediately you feel hot, My Lady.

0:07:33.620,0:07:36.260
We will make the utmost effort
to accommodate your needs, My Lady.

0:07:37.000,0:07:38.640
Thank you for your hard work, Mr Huang.

0:07:38.640,0:07:42.920
May I trouble you to inform His Majesty that
I will visit him shortly to thank him in person?

0:07:42.920,0:07:45.960
With the greatest pleasure, My Lady.

0:07:45.960,0:07:49.780
But I'm afraid His Majesty
is going to practice mounted archery.

0:07:49.780,0:07:52.940
You might want to go at a later time, My Lady.

0:07:52.940,0:07:56.100
Mounted archery?
Who did His Majesty go with?

0:07:56.100,0:07:58.500
Noble Prince Guo and Lady Cao.

0:07:58.500,0:07:59.700
Lady Cao?

0:07:59.700,0:08:04.780
Princess Wenyi has been feeling better.
His Majesty wished to see her.

0:08:08.540,0:08:12.320
His Majesty is very fond of the Summer Palace.
I'm excited to be here for the first time.

0:08:12.320,0:08:14.620
My Lady, I heard that Consort Honnête came as well.

0:08:14.620,0:08:16.740
I wonder what Her Highness looks like.

0:08:16.740,0:08:20.940
Consort Honnête has been bed-ridden for years.
We will get to see her sooner or later.

0:08:23.000,0:08:24.500
What is it?

0:08:28.500,0:08:30.040
What exceptional archery!

0:08:30.040,0:08:33.700
The wild pigeons in west Beijing are known for their swiftness.

0:08:33.700,0:08:37.580
But the archer caught two pigeons with one shot.

0:08:38.500,0:08:40.000
Peace to Lady Sourire.

0:08:40.140,0:08:42.260
Is it His Majesty who is practicing archery?

0:08:42.260,0:08:45.660
Noble Prince Guo came to visit.
His Lordship hunted game with His Majesty.

0:08:46.600,0:08:48.800
The veritable Noble Prince.

0:08:48.900,0:08:55.980
Vermilion told me that His Majesy pretended
to be Noble Prince Guo when he met you in the garden.

0:08:55.980,0:08:57.880
Now we get to see the real person.

0:08:58.000,0:08:59.900
His Majesty is an excellent archer.

0:08:59.900,0:09:02.980
It was Noble Prince Guo.
His Majesty was full of praise for His Lordship's archery skills.

0:09:03.000,0:09:05.960
Noble Prince Guo is known
for his achievement in the four arts.

0:09:05.960,0:09:07.720
It's a surprise that he excels at archery as well.

0:09:07.720,0:09:11.240
Ma'am, you'll discover His Lordship's
incredible versatility as you stay longer in the palace.

0:09:11.240,0:09:14.480
Xiao-Xiazi, you should bring back
the pigeons immediately.

0:09:14.480,0:09:18.540
And please inform His Majesty that I will pay respect
to him when he returns to the Governance Hall.

0:09:18.540,0:09:20.240
Allow me to take my leave.

0:09:22.900,0:09:27.160
I remember it was father who taught you archery.

0:09:28.400,0:09:31.140
Your Majesty's archery shifu was
the greatest baturu [Machu warrior].

0:09:31.300,0:09:37.520
My dull mind, however, didn't learn much from father.

0:09:37.800,0:09:44.160
What barturu taught was archery skills;
what father gave was parental love.

0:09:45.480,0:09:48.920
Father took a greater liking to you.

0:09:51.400,0:09:54.600
"Before heaven bestows great responsibilities upon a man,
it frustrates his spirit and will."

0:09:54.600,0:09:59.300
I ended up being a useless person
because of father's indulgence.

0:10:07.900,0:10:11.220
You've had a long day.
You should go have some rest.

0:10:11.220,0:10:13.000
I shall return to the Governance Hall.

0:10:14.200,0:10:15.860
His Majesty is leaving.

0:10:15.860,0:10:17.560
I bid Your Majesty goodbye.

0:10:27.800,0:10:29.820
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:10:29.820,0:10:31.240
Good, you're here.

0:10:33.720,0:10:40.420
Prince XVII, with all his might, managed to
acquire half a catty of "snow-grown greens".

0:10:40.420,0:10:42.380
It is well worth the effort.

0:10:42.380,0:10:44.460
You should try it.

0:10:45.000,0:10:47.040
You Majesty seems to be in a great mood.

0:10:48.520,0:10:53.400
I heard that the "snow-grown greens" can only
be found on precipices in the farthest north.

0:10:53.560,0:10:55.720
There are hardly more than ten trees
of the kind all around the world.

0:10:55.720,0:11:00.120
Nourished by the snow,
the tea has a refreshingly icy taste.

0:11:00.120,0:11:02.100
What efforts must His Lordship have devoted!

0:11:02.100,0:11:04.480
- Xiao-Xiazi.
- Yes.

0:11:05.740,0:11:13.080
On top of that, he even made the effort
to send me the tea on such a blazing day.

0:11:13.080,0:11:15.000
The thought matters more than the gift itself.

0:11:15.140,0:11:21.800
His Majesty was concerned about the costs
if he receives the tea every year.

0:11:22.500,0:11:26.140
While His Lordship is a thoughtful person,
Your Majesty thinks for the long term.

0:11:26.300,0:11:29.980
Lady Sourire, you hit the nail on the head.

0:11:33.020,0:11:37.400
I learnt that Your Majesty had just
had an enjoyable hunt with His Lordship.

0:11:37.400,0:11:39.860
I wonder where His Lordship is.

0:11:39.860,0:11:44.480
His Lordship must have heard of your supernal beauty,
so he has to avoid meeting you.

0:11:45.200,0:11:47.220
I am immensely flattered.

0:11:47.300,0:11:50.300
Your Majesty need not think of an excuse for him.

0:11:50.300,0:11:53.100
His Lordship must have known that
I look like Wuyan, the ugly woman from Qi.

0:11:53.100,0:11:55.340
So he had to escape before I come.

0:11:56.120,0:11:57.420
Did you hear that?

0:11:57.420,0:12:06.280
If she looked like Wuyan,
what would the other concubines look like?

0:12:06.980,0:12:10.440
Sourire was just joking.

0:12:11.120,0:12:13.820
Have some tea.

0:12:21.100,0:12:22.820
This is veritable good tea.

0:12:23.660,0:12:25.880
It has a refreshing taste and aroma.

0:12:25.880,0:12:28.000
What a thoughtful gift from His Lordship!

0:12:28.300,0:12:31.940
I was told that when Your Majesty first met Sourire,

0:12:31.940,0:12:37.340
you made her believe that you were Prince XVII
and enjoyed music with her in the garden.

0:12:37.340,0:12:41.000
That led to your happy relationship today,
which is so romantic a tale in the palace.

0:12:42.600,0:12:45.500
How did you know of such a private affair?

0:12:45.500,0:12:47.520
You must have heard it from His Majesty.

0:12:47.520,0:12:49.500
I didn't say anything.

0:12:50.480,0:12:55.580
Qinmo had an attentive ear to have heard the story.

0:12:55.580,0:13:02.000
In that case, Prince XVII is the
matchmaker for Your Majesty.

0:13:03.440,0:13:06.180
Prince Matchmaker is renowned
for his unrestrained talent.

0:13:06.180,0:13:11.620
Many a girl from the most distinguished families
admires and desires His Lordship.

0:13:11.620,0:13:18.160
Sourire, I believe you must have heard of
His Lordship in your maiden years.

0:13:23.780,0:13:30.280
I was living an isolated life before the Selection,
and held in quarantine after I moved in.

0:13:30.280,0:13:34.080
I never had a chance to hear about His Lordship.

0:13:37.020,0:13:41.700
Your Majesty is a laureate in literature,
and most considerate to the concubines.

0:13:41.880,0:13:46.300
I wonder if Your Majesty did the same
to approach Lady Cao.

0:13:53.440,0:13:56.420
Wenyi must be feeling hungry at this time.

0:13:56.420,0:14:00.080
Allow me to go and see to her lunch.

0:14:00.080,0:14:01.900
All right.

0:14:01.900,0:14:06.180
Wenyi is still crying a lot lately.

0:14:06.180,0:14:12.020
Ask Dr Jiang what the problem is
the next time he visits you.

0:14:12.020,0:14:16.440
Certainly, I will report yo Your Majesty after that.

0:14:42.220,0:14:46.640
This zither was treasured by Consort Dowager Serein.

0:14:46.640,0:14:51.100
I was craving for zither music before you arrived.

0:14:51.100,0:14:55.000
But Lady Cao was just aptly like
her name Qinmo [a quiet lyre].

0:14:55.000,0:14:58.320
She didn't play well.

0:15:02.100,0:15:04.280
I shall send for Meizhuang.

0:15:04.280,0:15:06.600
She is a brilliant zither player.

0:15:06.880,0:15:10.320
Meizhuang is able to play faultlessly,

0:15:10.500,0:15:14.540
but her music is somewhat emotionless.

0:15:14.700,0:15:20.740
Emotionless music is dull
however good a zither plays it.

0:15:22.100,0:15:24.920
Will you play the zither for me.

0:15:26.000,0:15:29.000
With pleasure, Your Majesty.

0:15:45.140,0:15:48.380
So crisp and clear is the sound of the zither!

0:15:55.100,0:15:59.600
A cup of tea with zither as wind ruffles the water.

0:15:59.900,0:16:02.600
Such is a pleasure in life.

0:16:03.340,0:16:06.960
Will you play the fist verse of  The Mountain Life.

0:16:28.620,0:16:30.220
I disappointed Your Majesty.

0:16:30.700,0:16:33.000
I hope I did not incur ridicule for my poor playing.

0:16:33.200,0:16:36.960
The playing was fine.
You were simply abstracted.

0:16:38.000,0:16:41.060
You did not devote all your heart to the zither.

0:16:42.500,0:16:46.500
I do beg Your Majesty's pardon
for my failure to commit to the music.

0:16:46.500,0:16:50.320
It was your first time playing the zither.
I understand that you were unacquainted with it.

0:16:53.500,0:16:57.180
But I have another question in mind.

0:16:58.140,0:17:01.640
Your love for me, I can clearly perceive.

0:17:02.880,0:17:07.700
But I was wondering when you began to feel love for me.

0:17:16.000,0:17:20.280
What I see is the person now sitting before me

0:17:20.400,0:17:22.400
regardless of his name or title.

0:17:22.840,0:17:23.900
What do you mean?

0:17:25.000,0:17:30.100
When Your Majesty, in the name of His Lordship,
extended your appreciation for my music in the garden,

0:17:30.280,0:17:39.220
I kept a respectful distance
even though I admired your flair.

0:17:40.480,0:17:43.940
After disclosing your identity,
Your Majesty took greater care of me

0:17:44.000,0:17:46.740
and treated me differently from the other concubines.

0:17:48.020,0:17:52.940
That is why I not only see Your Majesty
as the monarch, but also as my husband.

0:17:55.700,0:17:59.540
If I must tell Your Majesty the exact time,

0:18:00.800,0:18:06.540
it was when Your Majesty helped me out
when I was cornered by Yu in the garden.

0:18:07.600,0:18:09.800
I was utterly flustered at that moment.

0:18:09.800,0:18:12.940
While it was as easy as lifting a finger for Your Majesty,

0:18:13.620,0:18:18.400
in my eyes, Your Majesty was my savior.

0:18:27.500,0:18:30.740
I was just asking.

0:18:30.740,0:18:32.780
I hope Your Majesty would allow me to finish.

0:18:34.460,0:18:37.720
This might be a capital offence to Your Majesty.

0:18:38.620,0:18:41.200
I do revere you as the emperor,

0:18:41.200,0:18:47.260
but I regard you more as my loving husband.

0:18:54.700,0:18:57.740
I have always known that.

0:18:57.740,0:19:00.680
That is why I hold you dear to my heart.

0:19:00.700,0:19:05.500
Huan Huan, I was having undue suspicions.

0:19:06.500,0:19:08.500
Please don't blame me.

0:19:22.560,0:19:24.020
Si Lang.

0:19:30.000,0:19:34.500
My Lady, do you feel that someone revealed
your personal anecdote to Lady Cao?

0:19:35.300,0:19:38.220
It is just a doubt that I have.
There's no evidence.

0:19:39.000,0:19:44.520
(sigh) But only people closest to you would know such a tidbit.

0:19:44.520,0:19:47.400
I wasn't aware of it until today.

0:19:48.440,0:19:52.180
I believe Vermilion was the only witness in the garden.

0:19:53.380,0:19:57.200
But she is a dowry maid of yours, My Lady.

0:19:57.300,0:19:58.700
I know.

0:19:58.800,0:20:02.900
But I have confidence in Vermilion
after all these years living with her.

0:20:02.900,0:20:04.360
Yes, indeed.

0:20:04.360,0:20:07.440
She will never collude with Cao Qinmo against me.

0:20:08.740,0:20:10.600
I agree, My Lady.

0:20:10.600,0:20:16.260
Vermilion is a straightforward girl.
She might have brought it up to someone else.

0:20:17.340,0:20:19.760
But her unintentional words fell on a purposeful ear

0:20:19.760,0:20:24.260
so that the tidbit was passed on to Lady Cao.

0:20:25.300,0:20:28.860
That might be the only way to explain it.

0:20:30.820,0:20:32.800
It was fortunate that His Majesty trusted me.

0:20:32.800,0:20:37.800
Otherwise, I would be a goner
in face of the repeated rumor.

0:20:37.800,0:20:39.700
Absolutely.

0:20:39.800,0:20:44.280
Above all else, you've earned His Majesty's trust, My Lady.

