0:20:56.300,0:21:02.640
At Your Majesty's behest, I have instructed the
Imperial Kitchen to reduce the food ration for every palace

0:21:02.640,0:21:04.320
and increase the use of vegetables.

0:21:04.400,0:21:10.540
Very well. I must set an example
as His Majesty requires frugality in the harem.

0:21:10.540,0:21:11.980
Certainly.

0:21:13.000,0:21:15.680
As for the highest-ranking concubines,
Consort Fleur and Consort Astuce,

0:21:15.680,0:21:17.500
they will have to have the same ration as mine

0:21:17.680,0:21:20.200
so that the other concubines may willingly follow suit.

0:21:20.200,0:21:21.580
That is a great idea, Your Majesty.

0:21:21.800,0:21:23.600
It was not my idea.

0:21:23.600,0:21:26.980
It was Lady Shen who brought it up to His Majesty.

0:21:26.980,0:21:31.320
I must not take the credit for her kind thought.

0:21:41.940,0:21:45.800
Your Highness, I brought you
desserts from the Imperial Kitchen.

0:21:48.700,0:21:50.400
It's all right to have less desserts,

0:21:50.400,0:21:53.140
but they should at least make the crab puffs for me!

0:21:53.140,0:21:56.200
The kitchen staff said that crab meat
is too expensive in the summer.

0:21:56.200,0:22:00.040
They will stop making such desserts
at the Empress's command.

0:22:00.500,0:22:02.740
They have already halved the daily ration.

0:22:02.740,0:22:04.880
What's all this small-mindedness with the desserts?

0:22:05.400,0:22:07.840
(huff) Your Highness, please don't be mad.

0:22:07.840,0:22:10.300
The Summer Palace is not as well-provided as home.

0:22:10.300,0:22:12.100
The Empress is always stingy.

0:22:12.200,0:22:14.220
You can count the concubines here on one hand.

0:22:14.220,0:22:16.200
How much can we possibly consume?

0:22:17.260,0:22:19.120
We've been having vegetarian meals all day.

0:22:19.120,0:22:21.040
Needle mushroom salad after smashed cucumbers.

0:22:21.040,0:22:23.060
I didn't even see a single piece of meat!

0:22:24.060,0:22:26.500
My appetite is already suppressed by the summer heat.

0:22:26.500,0:22:28.600
Now I don't even have to eat!

0:22:29.280,0:22:32.260
I learnt that it is the same with the Empress's palace.

0:22:34.900,0:22:38.960
It was all Lady Shen's idea. She suggested
to His Majesty that we halve the food ration.

0:22:40.820,0:22:45.300
She's not yet in the place to manage the palace.
But doesn't she know how to rule?

0:22:47.500,0:22:49.100
- Song Zhi.
- Yes.

0:22:49.100,0:22:50.620
Distribute some money among the servants.

0:22:50.620,0:22:57.480
They deserve to eat well on such a hot day.

0:23:16.100,0:23:21.060
Lunar made me some prune tea.
It tastes better than what the Imperial Kitchen makes.

0:23:21.060,0:23:22.560
You should try it!

0:23:23.300,0:23:26.500
You forgot that I don't like sour food, didn't you?

0:23:27.000,0:23:28.440
Oh, sorry about that.

0:23:28.440,0:23:30.980
In that case, I'll have yours.

0:23:31.700,0:23:34.740
My Lady, you've had four or five servings already.
It might cause stomach pain.

0:23:36.760,0:23:38.220
All right then.

0:23:38.220,0:23:40.900
I just couldn't help drinking it on a hot day.

0:23:41.400,0:23:43.460
Poria is very good at making prune tea.

0:23:43.460,0:23:44.720
Who is Poria?

0:23:44.720,0:23:47.560
She was sent to serve My Lady in the Summer Palace.

0:23:48.500,0:23:51.540
Princess Wenyi will have her
first birthday on the 19th of next month.

0:23:51.540,0:23:55.200
His Majesty wishes to hold a grand celebration for her.

0:23:55.880,0:23:59.380
His Majesty has been seeing Lady Cao
a lot lately because of Wenyi.

0:23:59.380,0:24:03.300
She has been complacent for
being unaffected by Consort Fleur.

0:24:03.980,0:24:07.720
I heard about what happened the day before last.

0:24:07.720,0:24:13.880
She aroused grave suspicion of you in just a few words.
That is not a person to be underestimated.

0:24:14.860,0:24:17.840
Fortunately, His Majesty trusted me.

0:24:18.500,0:24:26.240
(sigh) Whatever place we now hold in His Majesty's
affection, it is not secure until we have a child.

0:24:27.000,0:24:29.000
Consort Fleur is one good example.

0:24:29.000,0:24:34.940
Without a child, she was
deprived of her authority overnight.

0:24:34.940,0:24:40.000
It would be futile to live an infertile life in the palace.

0:24:40.000,0:24:42.180
You are different from them.

0:24:45.000,0:24:48.460
Well, I am different from them.

0:24:48.500,0:24:54.220
His Majesty still talks to Consort Astuce
for she is the mother of the Third Prince.

0:24:54.300,0:24:59.760
Same with Lady Cao and Attendant Joie, whose
daughters are loved just as dearly by His Majesty.

0:25:00.480,0:25:03.780
The mother of a beloved child will
always be cherished by His Majesty.

0:25:04.760,0:25:09.900
Otherwise, a concubine will be forgotten after
the ephemeral affection from His Majesty.

0:25:13.620,0:25:18.800
By my calculations, it has been almost a year
since your first service to His Majesty.

0:25:19.620,0:25:23.180
I wonder ... why it is taking so long.

0:25:24.360,0:25:27.760
His Majesty hardly visits the harem.

0:25:28.100,0:25:33.260
Now I have even less time to see His Majesty
as I'm helping Her Majesty with the palace affairs.

0:25:34.000,0:25:35.040
(sigh)

0:25:35.040,0:25:38.980
After all, I must harbor bad luck.

0:25:38.980,0:25:41.700
Nonsense, it has nothing to do with luck.

0:25:42.200,0:25:49.100
Consort Fleur won incomparable favor from His Majesty
even if she didn't have a child.

0:25:49.680,0:25:53.020
We'll have so many children to fill the room with joy.

0:25:53.020,0:25:54.900
Put your mind at ease.

0:25:55.480,0:25:58.720
Can I talk to you heart-to-heart?

0:25:58.800,0:26:04.400
While pregnancy seems to depend on the will of Heaven,
[the Heaven represents the emperor]

0:26:04.920,0:26:08.980
people propose when Heaven disposes.
There is something we can do.

0:26:11.480,0:26:14.560
It seems to me that
the visit of His Majesty is all that matters.

0:26:14.560,0:26:17.320
What is there for us to do?

0:26:25.620,0:26:26.880
May I help you, doctor?

0:26:27.500,0:26:33.220
My name is Liu Ben. I'm here for the routine checkup
when Dr Jiang is away for a family funeral.

0:26:34.000,0:26:36.500
I hope you won't mind waiting for a while.
My Lady is talking to Lady Sourire.

0:26:36.660,0:26:38.020
Certainly.

0:26:46.500,0:26:50.700
With a carrot and stick, Dr Jiang
finally agreed to give me this prescription.

0:26:51.340,0:26:54.380
Following his instructions,
you are guaranteed to have a boy.

0:26:54.380,0:26:56.920
You should start as well.

0:26:58.100,0:27:00.700
Who is this Dr Jiang?

0:27:00.700,0:27:02.700
Who else can it be?
Jiang Cheng.

0:27:02.800,0:27:06.480
He's an expert in gynecology.

0:27:06.900,0:27:08.920
Jiang Cheng?

0:27:09.000,0:27:12.640
His younger brother, Jiang Shen,
is the doctor of Lady Cao.

0:27:12.640,0:27:13.700
Exactly.

0:27:15.000,0:27:16.980
Can we trust his prescription?

0:27:16.980,0:27:18.120
Don't worry.

0:27:18.120,0:27:23.080
I have done an extensive background check on him.

0:27:23.500,0:27:29.640
They are half brothers whose mothers are on competitive terms.

0:27:29.640,0:27:32.160
Because of this, they clash like fire and water.

0:27:32.160,0:27:34.460
That is why I trust him.

0:27:34.460,0:27:36.120
In addition,

0:27:36.120,0:27:39.740
I looked into many medical books
before I decided to use the prescription.

0:27:39.740,0:27:41.800
But I can't help feeling skeptical.

0:27:42.760,0:27:46.400
I'll send for Dr Wen to look at the prescription.

0:27:47.100,0:27:50.400
Vermilion, can you make the trip
to see if Mr Wen is on shift today?

0:27:50.400,0:27:52.200
If so, bring him here right away.

0:27:52.340,0:27:56.560
My Lady, Lord Protector Sun is gravely ill.
Dr Wen was sent away to attend to him.

0:27:56.560,0:28:01.800
He will stay there until Lord Sun gets better.

0:28:01.800,0:28:03.340
When did Dr Wen go?

0:28:03.340,0:28:04.780
Yesterday afternoon.

0:28:04.780,0:28:08.160
Dr Wen left on short notice
because it was an emergency.

0:28:08.500,0:28:10.260
How coincidental!

0:28:10.260,0:28:13.560
Not to worry, I've had two doses already.

0:28:13.560,0:28:15.200
I trust it is fine.

0:28:15.300,0:28:17.460
You don't have to summon a brigade for it.

0:28:17.460,0:28:19.400
Yes, exactly.

0:28:19.540,0:28:22.620
I saw a doctor ready and waiting outside.

0:28:33.400,0:28:35.800
I shall go since a doctor is visiting you.

0:28:35.900,0:28:37.300
I'll see you tomorrow.

0:28:39.200,0:28:40.820
Vermilion.

0:28:41.980,0:28:43.700
Your servant bows in respect before his mistress.

0:28:50.700,0:28:53.560
Your doctor bows in respect before you, My Lady.

0:28:53.560,0:28:58.000
I don't remember seeing you before.

0:28:59.080,0:29:01.740
This is my first visit to you, My Lady.

0:29:01.900,0:29:05.480
You seem to have a Jizhou accent.

0:29:05.480,0:29:08.880
I was transferred from Jizhou just a few days ago.

0:29:10.000,0:29:13.960
How serendipitous!
I'm from Jizhou as well.

0:29:14.700,0:29:17.440
I feel deeply honored, My Lady.

0:29:19.180,0:29:21.680
Poria, brew a pot of Longjing tea.

0:29:21.680,0:29:22.840
Certainly.

0:29:26.520,0:29:29.460
Princess Wenyi will be one year old in half a month.

0:29:29.460,0:29:35.060
The first birthday is well worth a grand celebration.

0:29:35.060,0:29:43.400
Even though we are not in the palace, His Majesty
wishes to have it as memorable as possible.

0:29:44.360,0:29:47.440
I have instructed the Household Department
to prepare for the occasion.

0:29:51.560,0:29:53.380
I thank Your Majesties.

0:29:53.380,0:29:55.880
Wenyi and I will be eternally thankful.

0:29:56.660,0:30:01.140
We are grateful for your contribution to the family.
Please don't thank us.

0:30:02.200,0:30:05.280
It would be a blessing if
His Majesty has imperial heirs in plenty.

0:30:05.280,0:30:12.400
I hope every one of you can share the
responsibility to expand the family.

0:30:13.960,0:30:15.820
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:30:15.820,0:30:21.320
While we don't have many imperial heirs,
we get one more when we come to the Summer Palace.

0:30:22.160,0:30:25.700
Consort Fleur, don't speak of such a taboo subject.

0:30:27.640,0:30:31.760
I don't care if that's a taboo to you.

0:30:33.100,0:30:37.380
How can the son of a humble maid
be counted as an imperial heir?

0:30:37.980,0:30:40.960
While the Fourth Prince is the son of a humble maid,

0:30:40.960,0:30:44.680
he is still the son of His Majesty

0:30:44.800,0:30:47.920
and the brother of the Third Prince.

0:30:48.300,0:30:50.380
(snort) How does he deserve to?

0:30:51.000,0:30:54.500
All right. Why did you have to bring it up?

0:30:54.500,0:30:57.380
We all have been living  with His Majesty for a long time.

0:30:57.380,0:31:03.660
Even if you don't care about it being a taboo,
do you not care how His Majesty would feel?

0:31:05.440,0:31:07.100
Pardon me, Your Majesty.

0:31:07.100,0:31:12.920
You should spend more time helping
the Third Prince with his studies.

0:31:12.920,0:31:15.340
Thank you, Your Majesty.

0:31:16.000,0:31:20.960
The Third Prince has been
working into late night recently.

0:31:20.960,0:31:26.700
Very well, he must set
a good example as the eldest son.

0:31:26.900,0:31:32.320
Handwork doesn't necessarily
make him better than a low-born.

0:31:32.500,0:31:37.640
I heard the Fourth Prince reciting
poems by the lake on my way here.

0:31:37.640,0:31:41.520
He sounded so much better than his brother.

0:31:42.000,0:31:48.600
Eh? Your Majesty, I can't help wondering who
has been taking care of the motherless boy.

0:31:48.600,0:31:51.000
Why does he seem to be smarter
than his distinguished brother?

0:31:51.800,0:31:53.500
You ...

0:31:53.640,0:31:57.000
Don't forget your manners, Consort Fleur.

0:31:59.920,0:32:06.120
In principle, you should be promoted
when your daughter is one year old.

0:32:06.120,0:32:11.820
But we are on a tight budget
while faced with the likely outbreaks of wars.

0:32:11.820,0:32:16.520
His Majesty wishes to hold a
glorious ceremony for you afterwards.

0:32:16.520,0:32:19.240
I believe you would't mind the delay.

0:32:19.800,0:32:21.760
Certainly, Your Majesty.

0:32:21.760,0:32:24.740
I am truly grateful for His Majesty's generosity.

0:32:24.740,0:32:28.360
But my humble existence does not
deserve His Majesty's heavenly grace.

0:32:28.360,0:32:34.300
All I wish is to always see joy and peace
abide in Your Majesties.

0:32:34.300,0:32:40.340
His Majesty appreciates your understanding.
He sends Wenyi a pair of jade ruyi to place the pillow on.

0:32:41.780,0:32:45.900
I will have it sent to your palace.

0:32:45.900,0:32:48.360
I thank Your Majesty.

0:33:05.000,0:33:06.700
Madam Autumn!

0:33:08.500,0:33:11.060
Good heavens! Why did you come here?

0:33:11.060,0:33:12.640
Where are your maids?

0:33:12.640,0:33:15.000
They don't care about me.

0:33:15.140,0:33:17.300
May I pay respect to Her Majesty?

0:33:17.800,0:33:20.100
Her Majesty is having a nap.

0:33:20.600,0:33:22.640
May I pay respect to His Majesty?

0:33:23.400,0:33:26.220
You should go when His Majesty summons you.

0:33:27.000,0:33:28.780
Excuse me.

0:33:29.800,0:33:33.040
Escort the Fourth Prince back to his residence.

0:33:47.200,0:33:50.560
Your Majesty, peeling lotus seeds
might hurt your finger nails.

0:33:52.200,0:33:56.520
His Majesty likes lotus seeds.
I wish to do it for him.

0:33:56.800,0:34:00.300
I will make lotus seed sweet soup for His Majesty.

0:34:00.400,0:34:02.960
Your love for His Majesty is more precious than gold.

0:34:03.000,0:34:06.060
But love is not as important as having a child.

0:34:06.100,0:34:09.840
Your Majesty, the Fourth Prince dropped by.

0:34:10.000,0:34:11.700
Why did he come here?

0:34:11.700,0:34:13.480
He wished to see His Majesty.

0:34:13.480,0:34:17.860
Forget it. He'll only make a nuisance of himself.

0:34:17.900,0:34:19.880
His Majesty would be displeased.

0:34:20.000,0:34:24.380
The Fourth Prince is too young
to have lost his birth mother.

0:34:25.280,0:34:28.420
Are you suggesting that I foster the Fourth Prince?

0:34:28.600,0:34:34.120
I thought the Fourth Prince
might be an option for Your Majesty.

0:34:35.440,0:34:38.060
But he is the least favored child.

0:34:38.060,0:34:41.740
What's the use of fostering him?
It's all right.

0:34:44.200,0:34:47.800
The hot and humid weather caused pimples.

0:34:48.100,0:34:51.220
Look, here's one, and here's another.

0:34:51.400,0:34:57.260
Don't worry, that increases the rosiness of your fair skin.

0:34:58.060,0:35:02.300
Now that your pimples are gone,
you start to make fun of mine.

0:35:02.500,0:35:05.520
All right, I'll stop it.

0:35:05.700,0:35:08.720
I can give you the anti-acne formula if you like.

0:35:09.640,0:35:15.440
It was offered by Dr Liu Ben,
who happens to be from Jizhou as well.

0:35:15.440,0:35:19.060
That is how my pimples were cured.

0:35:20.200,0:35:23.500
But I've never heard of this doctor.

0:35:23.500,0:35:27.920
He was just transferred from Jizhou.
He is an experienced doctor.

0:35:27.920,0:35:30.100
It is always nice to know
someone from your hometown.

0:35:30.300,0:35:32.000
Is he trustworthy?

0:35:32.100,0:35:34.340
I think so.

0:35:35.700,0:35:37.340
That's good.

0:35:37.340,0:35:40.300
When it comes to selecting servants,
character matters more than skills.

0:35:40.300,0:35:43.280
We must ensure that they have a clear background.

0:35:43.400,0:35:45.240
I agree.

0:35:45.300,0:35:49.300
Now that we both have a trusted doctor,

0:35:49.300,0:35:51.500
we will have more assurance in the palace.

0:35:51.600,0:35:56.300
Did you ask him to review Dr Jiang's prescription?

0:35:56.300,0:36:00.260
Yes, he said it is a perfect formula.

0:36:05.080,0:36:06.400
For real?

0:36:09.060,0:36:10.680
Peace to Your Highness.

0:36:12.880,0:36:15.560
I thought that there was only
the three of us in the garden.

0:36:15.560,0:36:18.460
You two seem to be enjoying the day as well.

0:36:19.000,0:36:21.920
It's nice that the weather is not as hot today.

0:36:22.000,0:36:25.900
I'm glad that you are here, Sourire.
I was going to visit you later.

0:36:26.840,0:36:29.060
I wonder if there is anything I can do for you.

0:36:29.880,0:36:32.820
I wish to apologize for
my improper remark the other day.

0:36:32.820,0:36:35.380
I heard that it caused misgivings to His Majesty.

0:36:35.380,0:36:38.680
I had no intention of doing that.

0:36:38.680,0:36:42.500
I must ask for your forgiveness today.

0:36:42.640,0:36:44.180
It was nothing like that, Lady Cao.

0:36:44.180,0:36:47.200
I simply had a bit of banter with His Majesty.

0:36:47.200,0:36:49.180
It wasn't not a big deal.

0:36:49.300,0:36:55.460
His Majesty is very fond of Lady Sourire.
Bantering with His Majesty is all too common for her.

0:36:55.600,0:36:59.560
But it would be such a big deal if it was someone else.

0:36:59.560,0:37:02.180
How can we possibly compare to Lady Sourire?

0:37:02.300,0:37:07.540
We have to first see His Majesty
before we can banter with him.

0:37:07.540,0:37:11.400
All right, all right.
We shouldn't be standing here for a talk.

0:37:11.400,0:37:13.660
Please come to my place.

0:37:13.660,0:37:17.360
I have prepared tea and snacks
to apologize to Lady Sourire.

0:37:17.400,0:37:20.860
And I invited Consort Astuce
and Attendant Joie for this purpose.

0:37:20.860,0:37:24.220
I humbly wish that Lady Sourire would not decline.

0:37:24.300,0:37:26.320
Lady Shen,

0:37:26.320,0:37:29.720
I've always admired your talent for playing the zither.

0:37:29.800,0:37:33.520
"An entertaining host attracts visitors."

0:37:33.520,0:37:37.480
But I am such an inept hostess.

0:37:37.480,0:37:42.860
Lady Shen, I hope you don't mind
helping me keep my guests with your music.

0:37:45.320,0:37:48.100
I'm grateful for your invitation.

0:37:50.100,0:37:53.200
My Lady, the prune tea has been cooled down.

0:37:56.200,0:38:00.960
You brought on the refreshing tea
after the greasy dishes.

0:38:01.500,0:38:04.560
What a gracious hostess we have!

0:38:14.000,0:38:16.680
Aiyo, what is wrong, Lady Shen?

0:38:18.120,0:38:22.500
I probably had too much jade aspic than I should.
I'm feeling a little sick.

0:38:22.500,0:38:23.820
Sick?

0:38:25.000,0:38:27.840
But you were all right right now.

0:38:29.000,0:38:30.960
Have you been feeling nauseous recently?

0:38:31.200,0:38:36.260
I haven't been eating well due to the summer heat.

0:38:36.300,0:38:37.420
Ah?

0:38:37.420,0:38:41.900
Is that ... because of pregnancy?

0:38:47.120,0:38:50.600
Have you menstruated this month?

0:38:52.180,0:38:53.200
I ...

0:38:53.200,0:38:56.200
Aiya, we are sisters.

0:38:56.200,0:38:57.880
- You can tell us.
- Exactly.

0:38:57.880,0:39:01.780
It's been late for more than half a month.

0:39:02.560,0:39:04.200
She's very likely to be with child.

0:39:04.300,0:39:06.380
Your Highness, what do you think?

0:39:07.380,0:39:13.640
Eh? In addition to feeling sick,
have you been feeling indolent lately?

0:39:13.640,0:39:16.580
And ... and having a craving for spicy food?

0:39:18.180,0:39:22.900
Xiao-Weizi, send for the doctor.

0:39:23.000,0:39:25.440
Please bring Dr Liu Ben.

0:39:35.360,0:39:38.480
Grace to Your Majesty.
You were the first one to arrive, nonetheless.

0:39:38.500,0:39:41.060
Is it true that Lady Shen is with child?

0:39:41.060,0:39:43.820
I was just informed to come here as well.

0:39:43.820,0:39:47.740
I have ordered the Attendance Registry
to be sent here immediately.

0:39:47.800,0:39:49.440
- Let's go inside.
- Certainly.

0:39:54.000,0:39:56.160
His Majesty the Emperor.

0:39:57.420,0:40:00.200
- Peace to Your Majesties.
- Sit down, sit down.

0:40:03.720,0:40:05.440
Is it real?

0:40:07.340,0:40:10.060
Doctor, can you confirm whether Lady Shen is pregnant?

0:40:12.100,0:40:15.260
Congratulations to Your Majesty and Lady Shen!

0:40:15.260,0:40:19.200
Lady Shen has been pregnant for over a month.

0:40:20.360,0:40:23.920
Very well. All rise.

0:40:24.000,0:40:25.360
I thank Your Majesty.

0:40:25.360,0:40:27.660
Autumn, bring the Attendance Registry.

0:40:33.880,0:40:36.020
Your Majesty.

0:40:37.000,0:40:38.500
(Palace of Universal Happiness, Lady Shen,
9 pm to 3 am, March 16th)

0:40:43.020,0:40:44.620
It was a good date.

0:40:47.000,0:40:49.740
Who are the personal maids of Lady Shen?

0:40:51.600,0:40:52.820
Your Majesty.

0:40:52.900,0:40:58.560
You must take the best care of
Lady Shen as her personal maids.

0:40:58.560,0:41:01.460
Report to me daily on her diet and health.

0:41:01.460,0:41:03.000
Yes.

0:41:03.000,0:41:04.860
The Empress is as meticulous as always.

0:41:05.000,0:41:08.500
Your Majesty, now that Lady Shen is with child,

0:41:08.500,0:41:12.420
we must select an imperial doctor to attend to her.

0:41:12.800,0:41:16.580
Your Majesty, this is Dr Liu Ben.

0:41:16.580,0:41:21.140
He is a reliable doctor,
and he is from Jizhou as well.

0:41:21.140,0:41:23.360
I have confidence in him.

0:41:23.700,0:41:25.260
Just as well.

0:41:25.260,0:41:27.680
Nothing matters more than your health.

0:41:27.680,0:41:31.260
You must ensure the best care of yourself.

0:41:31.260,0:41:32.500
I will.

0:41:32.620,0:41:34.620
My apologies to Your Majesties.

0:41:34.620,0:41:37.860
I forgot to serve Your Majesties tea all this time.

